hopobject.body: I'm not working at the moment best online pharmacy store While saving the universe from arch enemy The Master, the Fourth Doctor fell from the gantry of a radio telescope, a tumble which triggered his regeneration. “It’s the end,” grinned long-serving Baker as he lay on the grass. “But the moment has been prepared for…” He summoned the mysterious, glowing, ghostly white “Watcher”, who merged with his body to form Peter Davison. “Welcome aboard,” said the newcomer. “I’m The Doctor, or will be if this regeneration works out.”
